DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

00-2341. Disciplinary Counsel v. Furth.

This matter is pending before the court and is scheduled for oral argument on April 3, 2001. On February 28, 2001, relator, Disciplinary Counsel, filed a motion to correct the record. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that the motion be, and hereby is, granted.
